{"tid":2118460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"讀專科就係成功人士？","createTime":"2020-07-21T13:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T14:49:38.000Z","uid":304995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"afe9e67406ba878686b6973a6459411b5a3476db","tid":2118460,"uid":304995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"好多人話要讀專科先搵到工賺錢<br />\n但前提係你要好鍾意嗰科<br />\n如果唔係你只係做死嗰科，根本冇得你揀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人自己係讀醫療專科畢業(非醫生護士) 做緊野 <br />\n但覺得自己興趣根本唔喺呢到<br />\n日日做到好辛苦 行屍走肉 <br />\n仲成日喊<br />\n但我根本冇退路 唔知點做好 唔想做呢份工做死幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應唔應該再讀書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔想再考dse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇高人指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac76ec84d38e7ccce00755565b0534294129eb3c","tid":2118460,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識得大把人為份糧做護士<br />\n對呢行完全冇興趣<br />\n未又係咁過<br />\n依家買車買樓<br />\n相反個班為興趣嘅人&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1ea73fdff27aa7c0305094a75a673507e4cbe7","tid":2118460,"uid":304995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac76ec84d38e7ccce00755565b0534294129eb3c","tid":2118460,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識得大把人為份糧做護士<br />\n對呢行完全冇興趣<br />\n未又係咁過<br />\n依家買車買樓<br />\n相反個班為興趣嘅人&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:07:34.000Z","msg":"做得唔開心 有錢又有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83409ddb2628b0f7e8af3c4d517e3f3f8b4a99b5","tid":2118460,